STURTEVANT, Respondent, v. ADAMS, Appellant. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, Third Department. November 30, 1897.)

Action by Daniel Sturtevant against Jerry Adams. No opinion. Judgment modified by deducting therefrom $71.94, and, as modified, affirmed, with costs to the appellant in this -court and in the county court.
